{"_id":"0214e9586b6c8bb5","name":"Unwavering Focus","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"featType":"species","benefit":"Impose a penalty to Skill Checks for Mind-Affecting effects that target you.","prerequisite":"Zabrak","special":"","normalText":"","sourcebook":"Star Wars Saga Edition","page":0,"tags":["feat","racial","species","species_opportunity"],"bonus_feat_for":["species-zabrak"],"uses":{"current":0,"max":0,"perDay":false},"costNumeric":null,"description":"<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Zabrak</p>\n<p><strong>Effect:</strong> Whenever you are targeted by a<br>Mind-Affecting<br>effect that requires a<br>Skill Check<br>against your<br>Will Defense<br>, as a<br>Reaction<br>you can impose a -2 penalty to that<br>Skill Check<br>.</p>\n<p><em>Source URL: https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Unwavering_Focus</em></p>\n<p><strong>Automation:</strong> Punted to GM/player handling. When this reaction applies, the player/GM should apply the -2 penalty to the incoming mind-affecting skill check manually.</p>","executionModel":"PASSIVE","subType":"STATE","abilityMeta":{"modifiers":[{"target":"defense.will","value":2,"type":"untyped","predicates":["defense.will"],"enabled":false,"priority":500,"description":"Feat: GM/player-managed; no automatic modifier is applied. Punted to GM/player handling. When this reaction applies, the player/GM should apply the -2 penalty to the incoming mind-affecting skill check manually.","mechanicsMode":"gm_managed","applicationScope":"table_adjudicated","staticSheetPolicy":"exclude","requiresRuntimeContext":true,"requiresSelectedChoice":false,"predicateRequirements":["defense.will"],"conditionSummary":"Reaction: impose -2 on a mind-affecting skill check targeting your Will Defense."}],"mechanicsMode":"gm_managed","applicationScope":"table_adjudicated","staticSheetPolicy":"exclude","requiresRuntimeContext":true,"requiresSelectedChoice":false,"conditionSummary":"Punted to GM/player handling. When this reaction applies, the player/GM should apply the -2 penalty to the incoming mind-affecting skill check manually.","predicateRequirements":["defense.will"],"metadataPhase":"phase23-feat-cleanup","metadataNotes":"Phase 12 continues description-guided feat implementation by replacing false scaffold bonuses with explicit roll options, contextual predicates, resource/rider metadata, or supported static rules.","status":"gm_managed_phase23","description":"Punted to GM/player handling. When this reaction applies, the player/GM should apply the -2 penalty to the incoming mind-affecting skill check manually.","gmManaged":true,"archived_reactionRules":[{"id":"unwavering_focus_penalty","type":"INCOMING_SKILL_CHECK_PENALTY","value":-2,"trigger":"mindAffectingSkillVsWill","action":"reaction","description":"Impose -2 on a mind-affecting skill check made against your Will Defense."}]},"shortSummary":"Impose a penalty to Skill Checks for Mind-Affecting effects that target you.","sourceUrl":"https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Unwavering_Focus","rawImport":{"name":"Unwavering Focus","url":"https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Unwavering_Focus","pageTitle":"Unwavering_Focus","htmlCachePath":"C:\\Users\\Owner\\Downloads\\swse_cache\\feats_html\\unwavering_focus.html","referenceBooks":[],"prerequisitesText":"Zabrak","prerequisites":["Zabrak"],"effect":"Whenever you are targeted by a\nMind-Affecting\neffect that requires a\nSkill Check\nagainst your\nWill Defense\n, as a\nReaction\nyou can impose a -2 penalty to that\nSkill Check\n.","benefit":"","normal":"","special":"","indexPrerequisites":"Zabrak","indexBenefit":"Impose a penalty to Skill Checks for Mind-Affecting effects that target you.","indexPage":"Specialization_Feats","indexSection":"Species Feats","indexReferenceBooks":["Star Wars Saga Edition Rebellion Era Campaign Guide"],"sections":[],"rawText":"Reference Book:\nStar Wars Saga Edition Rebellion Era Campaign Guide\n\nSee also:\nFeats\n,\nSpecies Feats\n\nOthers might try to sway you, but once you focus on an objectiv