{"_id":"2bb34366776f0371","name":"Cut the Red Tape","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"featType":"general","benefit":"You can use your Knowledge (Bureaucracy) modifier instead of your Gather Information modifier when making Gather Information checks. If you are entitled to a Gather Information check reroll, you can reroll your Knowledge (Bureaucracy) check instead (subject to the same circumstances and limitations). You are considered Trained in the Gather Information skill for the purposes of this check.","prerequisite":"Trained in Knowledge (Bureaucracy)","special":"","normalText":"","sourcebook":"Galaxy of Intrigue","page":17,"tags":["feat","general","skill_gather_information","skill_knowledge","skill_synergy","social","skill_use_substitution","execution_mapped_phase8"],"bonus_feat_for":[],"uses":{"current":0,"max":0,"perDay":false},"costNumeric":null,"description":"<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Trained<br>in<br>Knowledge (Bureaucracy)</p>\n<p><strong>Effect:</strong> You can use your<br>Knowledge (Bureaucracy)<br>modifier instead of your<br>Gather Information<br>modifier when making<br>Gather Information<br>checks. If you are entitled to a<br>Gather Information<br>check reroll, you can reroll your<br>Knowledge (Bureaucracy)<br>check instead (subject to the same circumstances and limitations). You are considered<br>Trained<br>in the<br>Gather Information<br>skill for the purposes of this check.</p>\n<p><em>Source URL: https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Cut_the_Red_Tape</em></p>","executionModel":"PASSIVE","subType":"STATE","abilityMeta":{"status":"skill_use_substitution_phase8","description":"Cut the Red Tape: Gather Information skill uses may be rolled with Knowledge (Bureaucracy).","skillUseSubstitutions":[{"id":"cut-the-red-tape-gather-information-with-bureaucracy","fromSkill":"gatherInformation","toSkill":"knowledgeBureaucracy","applications":["Gather Information","Quick Intel","Find Black Market Object","Analysis"],"description":"Use Knowledge (Bureaucracy) for Gather Information skill uses."}],"mechanicsMode":"conditional","applicationScope":"skill_or_grapple_context","staticSheetPolicy":"contextual_only","requiresRuntimeContext":true,"requiresSelectedChoice":false,"conditionSummary":"Current metadata is implemented through skill/grapple helper payloads rather than generic static modifiers.","predicateRequirements":[],"metadataPhase":"phase3-static-vs-context","metadataNotes":"Phase 3 classification separates true static sheet bonuses from roll/target/action/choice-specific mechanics."},"shortSummary":"Use Knowledge (Bureaucracy) in place of Gather Information.","prerequisitesText":"Trained in Knowledge (Bureaucracy)","referenceBooks":["Star Wars Saga Edition Galaxy of Intrigue"],"sourceUrl":"https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Cut_the_Red_Tape","effect":"You can use your\nKnowledge (Bureaucracy)\nmodifier instead of your\nGather Information\nmodifier when making\nGather Information\nchecks. If you are entitled to a\nGather Information\ncheck reroll, you can reroll your\nKnowledge (Bureaucracy)\ncheck instead (subject to the same circumstances and limitations). You are considered\nTrained\nin the\nGather Information\nskill for the purposes of this check."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"migratedToState":true,"migrationDate":"2026-03-08T18:22:17.380Z","detectedPredicates":[],"id":"swse.feat.cut_the_red_tape","featContentRefresh":{"source":"swse_feats.json","sourceUrl":"https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Cut_the_Red_Tape","updatedFields":["system.description.value","system.benefit","system.prerequisite","system.special","system.normalText","system.shortSummary"]}}}}
{"_id":"2bdb31b248f680e3","name":"Republic Military Training","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"featType":"general","benefit":"Once per encounter, as a Reaction, you gain Damage Reduction 10 against an incoming attack if you have Cover from the attacker. You can gain the Damage Reduction as long as you have Cover, even if your opponent uses Aim to ignore your Cover bonus to Reflex Defense.","prerequisite":"None","special":"","normalText":"","sourcebook":"Knights of the Old Republic Campaign Guide","page":29,"tags":["background_opportunity","cover_play","faction_training","feat","general","military","species_opportunity"],"bonus_feat_for":[],"uses":{"current":0,"max":0,"perDay":false},"costNumeric":null,"description":"<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> None</p>\n<p><strong>Effect:</strong> Once per encounter, as a<br>Reaction<br>, you gain<br>Damage Reduction<br>10 against an incoming attack if you have<br>Cover<br>from the attacker. You can gain the<br>Damage Reduction<br>as long as you have<br>Cover<br>, even if your opponent uses<br>Aim<br>to ignore your<br>Cover<br>bonus to<br>Reflex Defense<br>.</p>\n<p><em>Source URL: https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Republic_Military_Training</em></p>","executionModel":"PASSIVE","subType":"STATE","abilityMeta":{"modifiers":[{"target":"metadata","value":0,"type":"untyped","enabled":false,"priority":500,"description":"Reduce incoming damage while behind cover.","mechanicsMode":"metadata_only","applicationScope":"non_static_context","staticSheetPolicy":"exclude"}],"mechanicsMode":"conditional","applicationScope":"action_or_reaction_hook","staticSheetPolicy":"exclude","requiresRuntimeContext":true,"requiresSelectedChoice":false,"conditionSummary":"Reduce incoming damage while behind cover.","predicateRequirements":[],"metadataPhase":"phase14-next-feat-implementation-batch","metadataNotes":"Phase 14 continues description-guided feat implementation: Force-skill bonuses, attack rerolls, condition-track rules, weapon-family rules, and safe action/resource metadata.","executionModel":"PASSIVE","subType":"RULE","implementationStatus":"action_metadata_phase14","actionRules":[{"type":"COVER_DAMAGE_REDUCTION_REACTION"}]},"shortSummary":"When behind Cover, you can reduce the damage of an incoming attack.","prerequisitesText":"None","referenceBooks":["Star Wars Saga Edition Knights of the Old Republic Campaign Guide"],"sourceUrl":"https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Republic_Military_Training","effect":"Once per encounter, as a\nReaction\n, you gain\nDamage Reduction\n10 against an incoming attack if you have\nCover\nfrom the attacker. You can gain the\nDamage Reduction\nas long as you have\nCover\n, even if your opponent uses\nAim\nto ignore your\nCover\nbonus to\nReflex Defense\n."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"migratedToState":true,"migrationDate":"2026-03-08T18:22:17.380Z","detectedPredicates":[],"id":"swse.feat.republic_military_training","featContentRefresh":{"source":"swse_feats.json","sourceUrl":"https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Republic_Military_Training","updatedFields":["system.description.value","system.benefit","system.prerequisite","system.special","system.normalText","system.shortSummary"]}}}}
