{"_id":"5ba03b04f0f1c7d7","name":"Recovering Surge","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"featType":"general","benefit":"When you catch a Second Wind, you move +1 step on the Condition Track.","prerequisite":"None","special":"","normalText":"","sourcebook":"Rebellion Era Campaign Guide","page":22,"tags":["condition_track","cover_play","defense","execution_mapped_phase8","feat","general","recovery","resource_second_wind","second_wind","survivability"],"bonus_feat_for":[],"uses":{"current":0,"max":0,"perDay":false},"costNumeric":null,"description":"<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> None</p>\n<p><strong>Effect:</strong> When you catch a<br>Second Wind<br>, you move +1 step on the<br>Condition Track<br>.</p>\n<p><em>Source URL: https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Recovering_Surge</em></p>","executionModel":"PASSIVE","subType":"RULE","abilityMeta":{"modifiers":[{"target":"attack","value":0,"type":"untyped","predicates":[],"enabled":false,"priority":500,"description":"Recovering Surge is a Second Wind/resource rule, not an attack modifier.","mechanicsMode":"manual","applicationScope":"manual_or_unimplemented","staticSheetPolicy":"exclude","requiresRuntimeContext":false,"requiresSelectedChoice":false,"predicateRequirements":[],"conditionSummary":"Recovering Surge is a Second Wind/resource rule, not an attack modifier."}],"resourceRules":{"secondWind":[{"type":"CONDITION_RECOVERY_ON_USE","steps":1,"description":"Move +1 step on the Condition Track when catching a Second Wind."}]},"mechanicsMode":"passive_resource","applicationScope":"secondWind_resource","staticSheetPolicy":"resource_only","requiresRuntimeContext":true,"requiresSelectedChoice":false,"conditionSummary":"Catching Second Wind also improves your Condition Track by 1 step.","predicateRequirements":[],"metadataPhase":"phase8-feat-implementation-continuation","metadataNotes":"Phase 3 classification separates true static sheet bonuses from roll/target/action/choice-specific mechanics.","status":"second_wind_rule_phase8","description":"Recovering Surge: catching Second Wind also moves you +1 step on the Condition Track."},"resourceRules":{"secondWind":[{"type":"CONDITION_RECOVERY_ON_USE","steps":1}]},"shortSummary":"Move up the Condition Track when you catch a Second Wind.","prerequisitesText":"None","referenceBooks":["Star Wars Saga Edition Rebellion Era Campaign Guide"],"sourceUrl":"https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Recovering_Surge","effect":"When you catch a\nSecond Wind\n, you move +1 step on the\nCondition Track\n."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"migratedToState":true,"migrationDate":"2026-03-08T18:22:17.382Z","detectedPredicates":[],"id":"swse.feat.recovering_surge","featContentRefresh":{"source":"swse_feats.json","sourceUrl":"https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Recovering_Surge","updatedFields":["system.description.value","system.benefit","system.prerequisite","system.special","system.normalText","system.shortSummary"]}}}}
{"_id":"5bedd71f0eead6b9","name":"Martial Arts II","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"featType":"general","benefit":"Damage dealt by your Unarmed attacks increases by one die step. In addition, you gain a +1 dodge bonus to your Reflex Defense (Which stacks with the dodge bonus granted by the Martial Arts I Feat).","prerequisite":"Martial Arts I, Base Attack Bonus +3.","special":"A situation that makes you lose your Dexterity bonus to Reflex Defense (If any) also makes you lose any dodge bonuses. Also, dodge bonuses stack with each other, unlike most other types of bonuses.","normalText":"The amount of damage you deal with a successful Unarmed attack is based on your size: Small, 1d3; Medium, 1d4; Large, 1d6.","sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":86,"tags":["feat","general","martial_style","offense_melee","unarmed","unarmed_damage_step","unarmed_damage_scaling"],"bonus_feat_for":[],"uses":{"current":0,"max":0,"perDay":false},"costNumeric":null,"description":"<p><strong>Reference Book:</strong> Star Wars Saga Edition Core Rulebook</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Martial Arts I<br>,<br>Base Attack Bonus<br>+3.</p>\n<p><strong>Effect:</strong> Damage dealt by your<br>Unarmed<br>attacks increases by one die step. In addition, you gain a +1 dodge bonus to your<br>Reflex Defense<br>(Which stacks with the dodge bonus granted by the<br>Martial Arts I<br>Feat).</p>\n<p><strong>Normal:</strong> The amount of damage you deal with a successful<br>Unarmed<br>attack is based on your size: Small, 1d3; Medium, 1d4; Large, 1d6.</p>\n<p><strong>Special:</strong> A situation that makes you lose your<br>Dexterity<br>bonus to<br>Reflex Defense<br>(If any) also makes you lose any dodge bonuses. Also, dodge bonuses stack with each other, unlike most other types of bonuses.</p>\n<p><em>Source URL: https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Martial_Arts_II</em></p>","prerequisitesStructured":{"type":"all","conditions":[{"type":"bab","min":3}],"_source":"canonical-csv"},"executionModel":"PASSIVE","subType":"MODIFIER","abilityMeta":{"modifiers":[{"target":"defense.reflex","value":1,"type":"dodge","enabled":true,"priority":500,"description":"Martial Arts II: +1 dodge bonus to Reflex Defense","mechanicsMode":"passive","applicationScope":"static_actor_and_unarmed_rule_hook","staticSheetPolicy":"include","requiresRuntimeContext":false,"requiresSelectedChoice":false,"predicateRequirements":[],"conditionSummary":"Always-on Reflex Defense dodge bonus; unarmed damage portion is handled by rule hooks."}],"rules":[{"type":"UNARMED_DAMAGE_STEP","params":{"steps":1},"description":"Martial Arts II: increase unarmed attack damage by one die step"}],"mechanicsMode":"passive","applicationScope":"static_actor_and_unarmed_rule_hook","staticSheetPolicy":"include","requiresRuntimeContext":false,"requiresSelectedChoice":false,"conditionSummary":"Always-on Reflex Defense dodge bonus; unarmed damage portion is handled by rule hooks.","predicateRequirements":[],"metadataPhase":"phase3-static-vs-context","metadataNotes":"Phase 3 classification separates true static sheet bonuses from roll/target/action/choice-specific mechanics."},"shortSummary":"Increases damage from Unarmed attacks by one die step; gain +1 bonus to Reflex Defense.","prerequisitesText":"Martial Arts I, Base Attack Bonus +3.","referenceBooks":["Star Wars Saga Edition Core Rulebook"],"sourceUrl":"https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Martial_Arts_II","effect":"Damage dealt by your\nUnarmed\nattacks increases by one die step. In addition, you gain a +1 dodge bonus to your\nReflex Defense\n(Which stacks with the dodge bonus granted by the\nMartial Arts I\nFeat)."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"id":"swse.feat.martial_arts_ii","featContentRefresh":{"source":"swse_feats.json","sourceUrl":"https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Martial_Arts_II","updatedFields":["system.description.value","system.benefit","system.prerequisite","system.special","system.normalText","system.shortSummary"]}}}}
{"_id":"5bef5e65e532ba7c","name":"Wicked Strike","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"featType":"general","benefit":"When you damage a target with a single, non- Area Attack using the Rapid Strike Feat, once per turn on your turn, you can immediately make a second attack at a -2 penalty against a second target within your reach. If this attack hits, you deal half of the original attack's damage to that target.","prerequisite":"Rapid Strike","special":"","normalText":"","sourcebook":"Scum and Villainy","page":30,"tags":["feat","general","offense","offense_melee"],"bonus_feat_for":[],"uses":{"current":0,"max":0,"perDay":false},"costNumeric":null,"description":"<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Rapid Strike</p>\n<p><strong>Effect:</strong> When you damage a target with a single, non-<br>Area Attack<br>using the<br>Rapid Strike<br>Feat, once per turn on your turn, you can immediately make a second attack at a -2 penalty against a second target within your reach. If this attack hits, you deal half of the original attack&#x27;s damage to that target.</p>\n<p><em>Source URL: https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Wicked_Strike</em></p>","executionModel":"PASSIVE","subType":"STATE","abilityMeta":{"executionModel":"PASSIVE","subType":"RULE","mechanicsMode":"conditional","applicationScope":"rapid_strike_followup_attack","staticSheetPolicy":"roll_context_metadata","requiresRuntimeContext":true,"requiresSelectedChoice":false,"conditionSummary":"Wicked Strike adds a once-per-turn second attack at -2 against another target within reach after damaging with a non-area Rapid Strike attack.","predicateRequirements":[],"metadataPhase":"phase17-next-feat-batch","metadataNotes":"Phase 17 clears the remaining Phase 16 active backlog by implementing engine-supported skill/reroll/attack-option rules where possible, and explicitly reclassifying table-state/picker-heavy feats as manual, punted, or deferred instead of leaving them as unincorporated placeholders.","implementationStatus":"attack_option_phase17","description":"Wicked Strike adds a once-per-turn second attack at -2 against another target within reach after damaging with a non-area Rapid Strike attack.","modifiers":[{"target":"metadata","value":0,"type":"untyped","enabled":false,"priority":500,"description":"Wicked Strike adds a once-per-turn second attack at -2 against another target within reach after damaging with a non-area Rapid Strike attack.","mechanicsMode":"metadata_only","applicationScope":"rapid_strike_followup_attack","staticSheetPolicy":"exclude","metadataPhase":"phase17-next-feat-batch"}],"rules":[{"type":"ATTACK_OPTION","option":"wickedStrike","label":"Wicked Strike","control":"flag","requiresAttackType":"melee","requiresOption":"rapidStrike","excludesAreaAttack":true,"followupAttack":{"trigger":"damageWithRapidStrike","targetLimit":1,"targetRequirement":"secondTargetWithinReach","attackModifier":-2,"damageMode":"halfOriginalDamage"},"summary":"After damaging with Rapid Strike, make a second attack at -2 against another target within reach; hit deals half original damage."}]},"shortSummary":"Gain extra attack on a second target upon damaging the first target.","prerequisitesText":"Rapid Strike","referenceBooks":["Star Wars Saga Edition Scum and Villainy"],"sourceUrl":"https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Wicked_Strike","effect":"When you damage a target with a single, non-\nArea Attack\nusing the\nRapid Strike\nFeat, once per turn on your turn, you can immediately make a second attack at a -2 penalty against a second target within your reach. If this attack hits, you deal half of the original attack's damage to that target."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"migratedToState":true,"migrationDate":"2026-03-08T18:22:17.382Z","detectedPredicates":[],"id":"swse.feat.wicked_strike","featContentRefresh":{"source":"swse_feats.json","sourceUrl":"https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Wicked_Strike","updatedFields":["system.description.value","system.benefit","system.prerequisite","system.special","system.normalText","system.shortSummary"]}}}}
