{"_id":"75ce7688bdfb0b23","name":"Deceptive Drop","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"featType":"general","benefit":"During the Surprise Round, if you damage a Flat-Footed target, that target is also knocked Prone if your attack roll also exceeds the target's Fortitude Defense. The target adds its size modifier to its Fortitude Defense:\n\n- Colossal, +50;\n- Gargantuan, +20;\n- Huge, +10;\n- Large, +5;\n- Medium and smaller, +0.","prerequisite":"Trained in Initiative","special":"","normalText":"","sourcebook":"Scum and Villainy","page":22,"tags":["control","feat","general","knock_prone"],"bonus_feat_for":[],"uses":{"current":0,"max":0,"perDay":false},"costNumeric":null,"description":"<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Trained<br>in<br>Initiative</p>\n<p><strong>Effect:</strong> During the<br>Surprise Round<br>, if you damage a<br>Flat-Footed<br>target, that target is also knocked<br>Prone<br>if your attack roll also exceeds the target&#x27;s<br>Fortitude Defense<br>. The target adds its size modifier to its<br>Fortitude Defense<br>:<br><br>- Colossal, +50;<br>- Gargantuan, +20;<br>- Huge, +10;<br>- Large, +5;<br>- Medium and smaller, +0.</p>\n<p><em>Source URL: https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Deceptive_Drop</em></p>","prerequisitesStructured":{"type":"all","conditions":[{"type":"skillTrained","skill":"cb5493f65f0bdb62"}],"_source":"canonical-csv"},"executionModel":"PASSIVE","subType":"STATE","abilityMeta":{"modifiers":[{"target":"metadata","value":0,"type":"untyped","predicates":["target.is-prone"],"enabled":false,"priority":500,"description":"Deceptive Drop is a surprise-round rider: if you damage a flat-footed target and your attack roll also exceeds its size-adjusted Fortitude Defense, it is knocked prone.","mechanicsMode":"metadata_only","applicationScope":"surprise_round_flat_footed_rider","staticSheetPolicy":"exclude","requiresRuntimeContext":true,"requiresSelectedChoice":false,"predicateRequirements":["round.surprise","target.flat-footed","attack.when-hit"],"conditionSummary":"Rules text is conditional and current metadata has predicates. It must only apply when the runtime context satisfies those predicates."}],"mechanicsMode":"conditional","applicationScope":"surprise_round_flat_footed_rider","staticSheetPolicy":"exclude","requiresRuntimeContext":true,"requiresSelectedChoice":false,"conditionSummary":"Surprise-round rider only: damaged flat-footed targets may be knocked prone if the attack roll beats size-adjusted Fortitude. Never add to attack totals.","predicateRequirements":["round.surprise","target.flat-footed","attack.when-hit"],"metadataPhase":"phase25-suspect-feat-cleanup","metadataNotes":"Removed false +2 attack metadata; Deceptive Drop is not a normal attack bonus.","riderRules":[{"type":"DECEPTIVE_DROP_PRONE_RIDER","trigger":"surpriseRoundDamageFlatFootedTarget","secondaryCheck":"attackRollExceedsTargetFortitudePlusSizeModifier","effect":"targetProne","sizeFortitudeModifiers":{"mediumOrSmaller":0,"large":5,"huge":10,"gargantuan":20,"colossal":50},"description":"During the Surprise Round, if you damage a Flat-Footed target and your attack roll also exceeds the target's size-adjusted Fortitude Defense, the target is knocked Prone."}],"status":"rider_metadata_phase25"},"shortSummary":"Flat-Footed targets knocked Prone on Surprise Round.","prerequisitesText":"Trained in Initiative","referenceBooks":["Star Wars Saga Edition Scum and Villainy"],"sourceUrl":"https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Deceptive_Drop","effect":"During the\nSurprise Round\n, if you damage a\nFlat-Footed\ntarget, that target is also knocked\nProne\nif your attack roll also exceeds the target's\nFortitude Defense\n. The target adds its size modifier to its\nFortitude Defense\n:\n\n- Colossal, +50;\n- Gargantuan, +20;\n- Huge, +10;\n- Large, +5;\n- Medium and smaller, +0."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"migratedToState":true,"migrationDate":"2026-03-08T18:22:17.383Z","detectedPredicates":["target.is-prone"],"id":"swse.feat.deceptive_drop","featContentRefresh":{"source":"swse_feats.json","sourceUrl":"https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Deceptive_Drop","updatedFields":["system.description.value","system.benefit","system.prerequisite","system.special","system.normalText","system.shortSummary"]}}}}
{"_id":"75daa55c22ffed5e","name":"Covert Operatives","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"featType":"team","benefit":"Gain bonuses on Stealth checks when near allies.","prerequisite":"Trained in Stealth","special":"","normalText":"","sourcebook":"Star Wars Saga Edition","page":0,"tags":["ally_support","cover_play","defense","feat","skill_stealth","skill_synergy","stealth","survivability","team","teamwork","conditional_skill_bonus","execution_mapped_phase8","manual_resolution","teamwork_base_skill_bonus_phase15"],"bonus_feat_for":[],"uses":{"current":0,"max":0,"perDay":false},"costNumeric":null,"description":"<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Trained<br>in<br>Stealth</p>\n<p><strong>Effect:</strong> You gain a +3 competence bonus on<br>Stealth<br>checks. At the time you make a check, for each ally within 12 squares of you who also has this Feat, the competence bonus increases by +1 (to a maximum of +7).<br><br>Additionally, when you move more than your speed or more than twice you speed, reduce the penalties to<br>Stealth<br>checks by 2.</p>\n<p><em>Source URL: https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Covert_Operatives</em></p>","executionModel":"PASSIVE","subType":"STATE","abilityMeta":{"executionModel":"PASSIVE","subType":"RULE","mechanicsMode":"passive_with_manual_teamwork","applicationScope":"skill_roll_plus_manual_teamwork","staticSheetPolicy":"roll_context_only","requiresRuntimeContext":false,"requiresSelectedChoice":false,"conditionSummary":"Covert Operatives: +3 competence skill bonus applies normally; nearby-ally scaling and other battlefield/teamwork clauses are GM/player managed.","predicateRequirements":[],"metadataPhase":"phase15-next-feat-batch","metadataNotes":"Phase 15 avoids automating nearby-ally/battlefield positioning clauses; base skill bonuses are implemented where unambiguous and teamwork clauses are preserved as manual metadata.","implementationStatus":"base_skill_bonus_manual_teamwork_phase15","description":"Covert Operatives: base +3 competence skill bonus implemented; nearby-ally scaling and special teamwork clauses remain table-managed flavor/manual metadata.","skillCheckBonuses":[{"id":"covert-operatives","skillKey":"stealth","type":"competence","featName":"Covert Operatives","description":"Covert Operatives: +3 competence bonus to stealth checks. Nearby-ally scaling is manual/table-managed.","value":3}],"teamworkRules":[{"type":"SKILL_PENALTY_REDUCTION","skillKey":"stealth","applications":["moving more than speed","moving more than twice speed"],"reduction":2,"description":"Reduce Stealth movement penalties by 2 when moving more than speed or twice speed.","automation":"manual","manualResolution":true}]},"shortSummary":"Gain bonuses on Stealth checks when near allies.","sourceUrl":"https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Covert_Operatives","rawImport":{"name":"Covert Operatives","url":"https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Covert_Operatives","pageTitle":"Covert_Operatives","htmlCachePath":"C:\\Users\\Owner\\Downloads\\swse_cache\\feats_html\\covert_operatives.html","referenceBooks":[],"prerequisitesText":"Trained\nin\nStealth","prerequisites":["Trained\nin\nStealth"],"effect":"You gain a +3 competence bonus on\nStealth\nchecks. At the time you make a check, for each ally within 12 squares of you who also has this Feat, the competence bonus increases by +1 (to a maximum of +7).\n\nAdditionally, when you move more than your speed or more than twice you speed, reduce the penalties to\nStealth\nchecks by 2.","benefit":"","normal":"","special":"","indexPrerequisites":"Trained in Stealth","indexBenefit":"Gain bonuses on Stealth checks when near allies.","indexPage":"Specialization_Feats","indexSection":"Team Feats","indexReferenceBooks":["Star Wars Saga Edition Galaxy at War"],"sections":[],"rawText":"Reference Book:\nStar Wars Saga Edition Galaxy at War\n\nSee also:\nFeats\n,\nTeam Feats\n\nYou and your allies specialize in undercover missions in which stealth and subtlety are paramount.\n\nPrerequisite:\nTrained\nin\nStealth\n\nEffect:\nYou gain a +3 competence bonus on\nStealth\nchecks. At the time you make a check, for each ally within 12 squares of you who also has this Feat, the competence bonus increases by +1 (to a maximum of +7).\n\nAdditionally, when you move more than your speed or more than twice you speed, reduce the penalties to\nStealth\nchecks by 2."},"prerequisitesText":"Trained\nin\nStealth","effect":"You gain a +3 competence bonus on\nStealth\nchecks. At the time you make a check, for each ally within 12 squares of you who also has this Feat, the competence bonus increases by +1 (to a maximum of +7).\n\nAdditionally, when you move more than your speed or more than twice you speed, reduce the penalties to\nStealth\nchecks by 2."},"effects":[{"_id":"acf6131e-f0c7-4851-99dd-0f0efd6241b8","name":"Covert Operatives","icon":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{},"flags":{"swse":{"source":"feat","featName":"Covert Operatives","effectType":"skill_bonus","requiresCustomLogic":true}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"migratedToState":true,"migrationDate":"2026-03-08T18:22:17.383Z","detectedPredicates":["movement.while-moving","proximity.count-allies-within-12"],"id":"swse.feat.covert_operatives"}}}
