ncan be spent only to add to the result of a\nPerception\ncheck, and if it is not spent before the end of the encounter, it is lost."},"prerequisitesText":"Zabrak","effect":"Whenever you reroll a\nPerception\ncheck and take the second result, if your second result is lower than your first result, you gain a temporary\nForce Point\n. This\nForce Point\ncan be spent only to add to the result of a\nPerception\ncheck, and if it is not spent before the end of the encounter, it is lost."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"migratedToState":true,"migrationDate":"2026-03-08T18:22:17.387Z","detectedPredicates":[],"id":"swse.feat.instinctive_perception"}}}
{"_id":"c01f64239af7705d","name":"Extra Rage","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"featType":"general","benefit":"You can Rage one additional time per day.","prerequisite":"Rage Species Trait","special":"You can take this Feat multiple times; each time you take this Feat, you can Rage one additional time per day.","normalText":"","sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":86,"tags":["execution_mapped_phase9","feat","general","offense_melee","rage","resource_spend"],"bonus_feat_for":[],"uses":{"current":0,"max":0,"perDay":false},"costNumeric":null,"description":"<p><strong>Reference Book:</strong> Star Wars Saga Edition Core Rulebook</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Rage Species Trait</p>\n<p><strong>Effect:</strong> You can Rage one additional time per day.</p>\n<p><strong>Special:</strong> You can take this Feat multiple times; each time you take this Feat, you can Rage one additional time per day.</p>\n<p><em>Source URL: https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Extra_Rage</em></p>","executionModel":"PASSIVE","subType":"STATE","abilityMeta":{"status":"rage_rule_phase9","description":"Extra Rage: +1 additional Rage use per day.","rules":[{"type":"RAGE_USES_BONUS","value":1,"description":"Rage one additional time per day."}],"mechanicsMode":"conditional","applicationScope":"rage_context","staticSheetPolicy":"contextual_only","requiresRuntimeContext":true,"requiresSelectedChoice":true,"conditionSummary":"Only applies while the actor is raging or using rage-specific rules.","predicateRequirements":[],"metadataPhase":"phase3-static-vs-context","metadataNotes":"Phase 3 classification separates true static sheet bonuses from roll/target/action/choice-specific mechanics."},"shortSummary":"Rage one additional time per day.","prerequisitesText":"Rage Species Trait","referenceBooks":["Star Wars Saga Edition Core Rulebook"],"sourceUrl":"https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Extra_Rage","effect":"You can Rage one additional time per day."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"