{"_id":"dd2c0e394cdf08ba","name":"Mighty Swing","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"featType":"general","benefit":"You can spend two Swift Actions in the same round to deal +1 die of damage on your next melee attack in the same round.","prerequisite":"Strength 13","special":"The effects of this Feat do not stack with the extra damage provided by the Rapid Strike Feat.","normalText":"","sourcebook":"Galaxy at War","page":26,"tags":["action_economy","feat","general","offense","swift_action"],"bonus_feat_for":["f62ca2e639cab614"],"uses":{"current":0,"max":0,"perDay":false},"costNumeric":null,"description":"<p><strong>Reference Book:</strong> Star Wars Saga Edition Core Rulebook</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Strength<br>13</p>\n<p><strong>Effect:</strong> You can spend two<br>Swift Actions<br>in the same round to deal +1 die of damage on your next melee attack in the same round.</p>\n<p><strong>Special:</strong> The effects of this Feat do not stack with the extra damage provided by the<br>Rapid Strike<br>Feat.</p>\n<p><em>Source URL: https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Mighty_Swing</em></p>","prerequisitesStructured":{"type":"all","conditions":[{"type":"attribute","ability":"str","min":13}],"_source":"canonical-csv"},"executionModel":"PASSIVE","subType":"STATE","abilityMeta":{"status":"attack_option_phase7_refined","description":"Mighty Swing: exposed through CombatOptionResolver; not applied as a passive sheet modifier.","rules":[{"type":"ATTACK_OPTION","option":"mightySwing","label":"Mighty Swing","summary":"Spend two swift actions to add one weapon damage die to your next melee attack this round.","control":"toggle","requiresAttackType":"melee","requiresSwiftActions":2,"damageExtraWeaponDice":1,"nonStackingWith":["rapidStrike"]}],"mechanicsMode":"active","applicationScope":"attack_option","staticSheetPolicy":"roll_context_only","requiresRuntimeContext":true,"requiresSelectedChoice":false,"conditionSummary":"Exposed as a deliberate combat option