{"_id":"f8748ba7993b6b17","name":"Sure Climber","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"featType":"species","benefit":"Gain a Climb Speed of 4 squares.","prerequisite":"Sullustan","special":"","normalText":"","sourcebook":"Star Wars Saga Edition","page":0,"tags":["execution_mapped_phase10","execution_mapped_phase9","feat","racial","skill_climb","skill_synergy","species","species_opportunity","species_rule"],"bonus_feat_for":["species-sullustan"],"uses":{"current":0,"max":0,"perDay":false},"costNumeric":null,"description":"<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Sullustan</p>\n<p><strong>Effect:</strong> Whenever you are not distracted or threatened, you gain a natural Climb Speed of 4 squares.</p>\n<p><strong>Normal:</strong> Without a Climb Speed, you must succeed on a<br>Climb<br>check to climb.</p>\n<p><em>Source URL: https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Sure_Climber</em></p>","executionModel":"PASSIVE","subType":"STATE","abilityMeta":{"status":"conditional_climb_metadata_phase25","description":"Sure Climber: climb speed 4 squares. Exposed as a movement mode hook.","rules":[{"type":"MOVEMENT_MODE_SET","mode":"climb","value":4,"unit":"squares","description":"Whenever you are not distracted or threatened, you gain a natural Climb Speed of 4 squares.","displayAsCondition":true,"displayLabel":"Sure Climber","displayNote":"Conditional capability: Climb Speed 4 squares only when not distracted or threatened.","gmEnforced":true}],"mechanicsMode":"metadata_only","applicationScope":"conditional_movement_capability","staticSheetPolicy":"display_condition_only","requiresRuntimeContext":true,"requiresSelectedChoice":false,"conditionSummary":"Conditional climb capability only: Climb Speed 4 squares when not distracted or threatened. Do not treat as always-on in combat.","predicateRequirements":["not.distracted","not.threatened"],"metadataPhase":"phase25-suspect-feat-cleanup","metadataNotes":"Reclassified from persistent movement include to metadata/display condition."},"shortSummary":"Gain a Climb Speed of 4 squares.","sourceUrl":"https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Sure_Climber","rawImport":{"name":"Sure Climber","url":"https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Sure_Climber","pageTitle":"Sure_Climber","htmlCachePath":"C:\\Users\\Owner\\Downloads\\swse_cache\\feats_html\\sure_climber.html","referenceBooks":[],"prerequisitesText":"Sullustan","prerequisites":["Sullustan"],"effect":"Whenever you are not distracted or threatened, you gain a natural Climb Speed of 4 squares.","benefit":"","normal":"Without a Climb Speed, you must succeed on a\nClimb\ncheck to climb.","special":"","indexPrerequisites":"Sullustan","indexBenefit":"Gain a Climb Speed of 4 squares.","indexPage":"Specialization_Feats","indexSection":"Species Feats","indexReferenceBooks":["Star Wars Saga Edition Rebellion Era Campaign Guide"],"sections":[],"rawText":"Reference Book:\nStar Wars Saga Edition Rebellion Era Campaign Guide\n\nSee also:\nFeats\n,\nSpecies Feats\n\nYou can navigate steep cliffs and caverns as though climbing were second nature to you.\n\nPrerequisite:\nSullustan\n\nEffect:\nWhenever you are not distracted or threatened, you gain a natural Climb Speed of 4 squares.\n\nNormal:\nWithout a Climb Speed, you must succeed on a\nClimb\ncheck to climb."},"prerequisitesText":"Sullustan","effect":"Whenever you are not distracted or threatened, you gain a natural Climb Speed of 4 squares."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"migratedToState":true,"migrationDate":"2026-03-08T18:22:17.389Z","detectedPredicates":[],"id":"swse.feat.sure_climber"}}}
{"_id":"f8e2a30390d870e7","name":"Improved Defenses","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"featType":"general","benefit":"You gain a +1 bonus to your Reflex Defense, Fortitude Defense, and Will Defense.","prerequisite":"None","special":"","normalText":"","sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":87,"tags":["defense","feat","general","survivability"],"bonus_feat_for":["f62ca2e639cab614","b5bed5d1b5f42958","8c58016e587dd2c7"],"uses":{"current":0,"max":0,"perDay":false},"costNumeric":null,"description":"<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> None</p>\n<p><strong>Effect:</strong> You gain a +1 bonus to your<br>Reflex Defense<br>,<br>Fortitude Defense<br>, and<br>Will Defense<br>.</p>\n<h3>Additional Improved Defenses Effects</h3><p>Reference Book:<br>Star Wars Saga Edition Starships of the Galaxy<br><br>Special:<br>This Feat does not apply to the<br>Defenses<br>of a<br>Vehicle<br>, even if you are piloting or commanding it. This is one reason many<br>Pilots<br>prefer the<br>Dodge<br>Feat to Improved Defenses.</p>\n<p><em>Source URL: https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Improved_Defenses</em></p>","executionModel":"PASSIVE","subType":"MODIFIER","abilityMeta":{"modifiers":[{"target":"defense.fortitude","value":1,"type":"untyped","enabled":true,"priority":500,"description":"Improved Defenses: +1 to Fortitude Defense","mechanicsMode":"passive","applicationScope":"static_actor","staticSheetPolicy":"include","requiresRuntimeContext":false,"requiresSelectedChoice":false,"predicateRequirements":[],"conditionSummary":"Always-on +1 to Fortitude, Reflex, and Will."},{"target":"defense.reflex","value":1,"type":"untyped","enabled":true,"priority":500,"description":"Improved Defenses: +1 to Reflex Defense","mechanicsMode":"passive","applicationScope":"static_actor","staticSheetPolicy":"include","requiresRuntimeContext":false,"requiresSelectedChoice":false,"predicateRequirements":[],"conditionSummary":"Always-on +1 to Fortitude, Reflex, and Will."},{"target":"defense.will"